data.description: Welcome to this charming and inviting 2-bedroom, 1-bathroom ground level condo, located in the heart of Marlow Heights.  This property boasts modern updates to closets, bathroom and kitchen, and bamboo flooring throughout with an open layout which is bright, cozy and inviting.  This property provides a comfortable space for relaxation and entertainment. The kitchen offers a dishwasher, efficient functionality, ample storage and countertop space with an opportunity for a personalized touch.  The two bedrooms are well-sized and provide versatility for a home office, guest room, or additional living space. The primary bedroom has a generous sized walk in closet. The hallway features 2 additional closets, one being a walk-in closet. Step outside onto the elongated patio to relax, unwind and enjoy some fresh air!  This condo is located in Marlow Towers, where residents enjoy an outdoor pool and unassigned parking. Located one mile from Suitland Metro station, and just minutes from National Harbor, Washington, DC, MGM, Alexandria, VA, I-495, I-695, and I-295.  Perfect for first-time buyers, downsizers, or those seeking a low-maintenance lifestyle, this cozy condo presents a wonderful opportunity to enjoy comfortable living in a convenient location, as gas, water and ground maintenance (and snow removal) are included in the condo fee.  This unit is also conveniently located directly across from the laundry room and storage facility. This property provides the owner with an opportunity to personalize and create a space tailored to their liking.  Schedule a showing today to experience the warmth, potential and charm this condo has to offer! If anyone is ill, has flu-like symptoms or recently been exposed to Covid-19 please do not show. Please follow all CDC Covid-19 guidelines when showing property. Thank you!
